dmca.title: TV DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google: Android Market

works.description:
A novel written by Bethan Reeks  
called 'The Kissing Booth', under contract with Random House Children's  
Books UK. Originally published on wattpad.com, "The Kissing Booth" can be 

viewed at the URL supplied. It is also being offered as an app on the  
Google Play store, which is not authorised by RHCP UK or by the author.
